    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The trimming or cutting away of edges, as portions of a photograph or printed page. To trim; cutting down prints, photographs, or pages to a required size, often without regard for their original composition.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
